            "description": "Create a staking vault for an approved project.\nMUST be called after approving the project — will fail on-chain if project is not APPROVED.\nA vault can only be created once per project (E_VAULT_ALREADY_EXISTS on retry).\n\nAfter creating the vault, deposit rewards before investors can claim APY.\n\nRequired fields:\n- project_id: ID of the APPROVED project to create a vault for\n- apy_rate: APY in basis points (1200 = 12%, 800 = 8%, 500 = 5%)"
          },
